_sText:
Glassassaultii_glasserver by Kopf sucht Kugel

This map is based on glassassaultii_alagrand_final.
It has been reloaded exclusive for glasserver.de
by Kopf sucht Kugel cause of the big advantage of the 
counter terrorist force. In the .bsp file are all data 
included, navigation file, text file, textures and 
last but not least the map overview.

I hope you will have fun on this nice reload.



P.S.: The best playercount for this map is between 12 an 14. With about 6 or 7 players in each team you will be able to defend your building and attack your enemy ones very well. I am happy for every positiv critic but sadly I wont change anything anymore because there are already 3 other version of my map and I dont want release one more of it. I hope you understand this. This map is running on glasserver.de:27015 nearly every day, may you join us and have some fun? =)

greetz
Kopf sucht Kugel
